Deep Learning in the context of Artificial Intelligence

Within AI, you have additional layers or machine learning, and brain-inspired learning. This is where neural networks come into play and within these neural networks lies deep learning.

Connections to a neuron in the brain. xi, wi, f(·), and b are the activations, weights, non-linear function and bias, respectively. Input is xo, x1 and x2 and output is y in the 
figure. 

